  <brief_title>Melatonin Supplementation for Delirium Prevention in Acutely Hospitalized Elderly</brief_title>
  <official_title>Melatonin Supplementation for Delirium Prevention in Acutely Hospitalized Elderly: a Randomized, Double Blind, Placebo-Controlled Trial</official_title>
